## STRING MANIPULATION
**Required Includes:** `#include <string>` (and `#include <cctype>` for `toupper`/`tolower`)
| Function Name | Purpose | Example / Output |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **`length()` / `size()`** | Returns the number of characters in the string. | `string s = "BPA"; s.length();` // *3* |
| **`empty()`** | Returns `true` if length is 0. Faster than `length() == 0`. | `string s = ""; s.empty();` // *true* |
| **`clear()`** | Wipes out all characters, making the string empty. | `string s = "BPA"; s.clear();` // *s is ""* |
| **`resize(n, char)`** | Changes string length. Fills new space with `char`. | `string s = "BPA"; s.resize(5, '!');` // *s is "BPA!!"* |
| **`at(index)`** | Safely gets the character at the index (throws error if out of bounds). | `string s = "BPA"; s.at(0);` // *'B'* |
| **`front()` / `back()`** | Gets the very first or very last character. | `string s = "BPA"; s.back();` // *'A'* |
| **`append()` / `+=`** | Adds a string to the end of the current string. | `string s = "Music"; s += " City";` // *s is "Music City"* |
| **`push_back(char)`** | Adds a **single character** to the end. | `string s = "Apple"; s.push_back('s');` // *s is "Apples"* |
| **`pop_back()`** | Deletes the **last character** of the string. | `string s = "Apples"; s.pop_back();` // *s is "Apple"* |
| **`insert(pos, str)`** | Inserts a new string starting at the given index. | `string s = "BPA"; s.insert(1, "x");` // *s is "BxPA"* |
| **`erase(pos, len)`** | Deletes a chunk of characters starting at `pos`. | `string s = "BPA"; s.erase(0, 1);` // *s is "PA"* |
| **`replace(pos, len, str)`**| Swaps a chunk of length `len` at `pos` with `str`. | `string s = "BPA"; s.replace(0, 1, "C");` // *s is "CPA"* |
| **`find(str)`** | Returns index of **first match**. Returns `string::npos` if not found. | `string s = "BPA"; s.find("P");` // *1* |
| **`rfind(str)`** | Returns index of **last match** (Reverse Find). | `string s = "file.txt"; s.rfind(".");` // *4* |
| **`find_first_of(str)`** | Finds first occurrence of **any character** in the provided string. | `string s = "BPA2026"; s.find_first_of("0123");` // *3* |
| **`find_first_not_of(str)`**| Finds first occurrence of any character **NOT** in the string. | `string s = "  BPA"; s.find_first_not_of(" ");` // *2* |
| **`substr(pos, len)`** | Extracts a sub-portion of the string. | `string s = "Nashville"; s.substr(0, 4);` // *"Nash"* |
| **`std::to_string(num)`** | Converts an integer or double into a string. | `int n = 5; to_string(n);` // *"5"* |
| **`std::stoi(str)`** | Converts a string into an integer (String To Int). | `string s = "10"; stoi(s);` // *10* |
| **`std::stod(str)`** | Converts a string into a double (String To Double). | `string s = "3.14"; stod(s);` // *3.14* |
| **`toupper(char)`** | Converts a single character to uppercase. | `char c = 'a'; toupper(c);` // *'A'* |
| **`tolower(char)`** | Converts a single character to lowercase. | `char c = 'A'; tolower(c);` // *'a'* |


